name: OpenMetrics endpoint health
description: Returns `CRITICAL` if the Agent is unable to connect to the OpenMetrics endpoint, otherwise returns `OK`.

name: Inference API endpoint health
description: Returns `CRITICAL` if the Agent is unable to connect to the Inference API endpoint or if it is unhealthy, otherwise returns `OK`.

name: Management API endpoint health
description: Returns `CRITICAL` if the Agent is unable to connect to the Management API endpoint, otherwise returns `OK`.
